# VEHICLE::SET_CARGOBOB_PICKUP_MAGNET_REDUCED_FALLOFF

## Summary
Set how the reduced force magnitude drops off as the distance to an entity increases

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **FLOAT** magnetFalloff
